info.name: Vienna Creamy Latte
info.description:

Serving size (ml)/Calories (kcal) - Short (237ml) - 330 kcal, Tall (354ml) - 446 kcal, Grande (473ml) - 545 kcal, Venti (591ml) - 675 kcal.
Allergen - Contains Milk.
